The problem is that you are trying to show 1740 points on the 800px width chart. It is not possible that each point will be plotted because there are more points than available pixels.

So the solution can be to use `chart.scrollablePlotArea`:

    Highcharts.chart(&#39;container&#39;, {
      chart: {
      	scrollablePlotArea: {
        	minWidth: 2000
        }
      },
      series: [{
        data
      }]
    });

**Demo:**

 - https://jsfiddle.net/BlackLabel/1mdq3p28/

**API reference:**

 - https://api.highcharts.com/highcharts/chart.scrollablePlotArea

